{
  "Phrases": [
    {
      "Text": {
        "Text": "*YOU! * You miserable, weaselly bastard - you'd dare to come back after so long?  After *abandoning* me to them?",
        "Flags": "Standard",
        "Sound": "",
        "VolumeVariance": 0,
        "PitchVariance": 0,
        "Strref": 8495
      },
      "ResponsesIndexFirst": 0,
      "ResponsesCount": 2,
      "TriggerIndex": 2,
      "Index": 0
    },
    {
      "Text": {
        "Text": "*YOU!*  You callous, wretched she-devil - you'd dare to come back after so long?  After *abandoning* me to them?",
        "Flags": "Standard",
        "Sound": "",
        "VolumeVariance": 0,
        "PitchVariance": 0,
        "Strref": 8498
      },
      "ResponsesIndexFirst": 2,
      "ResponsesCount": 2,
      "TriggerIndex": 3,
      "Index": 1
    },
    {
      "Text": {
        "Text": "What?!  What?!  Did you think you could just return, apologize, MAKE AMENDS?  Look at what's become of me as a result of your cowardice, damn you!  Look upon my shattered remains, broken on that rack!  LOOK AT ME!",
        "Flags": "Standard",
        "Sound": "",
        "VolumeVariance": 0,
        "PitchVariance": 0,
        "Strref": 8499
      },
      "ResponsesIndexFirst": 4,
      "ResponsesCount": 3,
      "TriggerIndex": -1,
      "Index": 2
    },
    {
      "Text": {
        "Text": "No... no, no, NO!  There'll be no escape for you, no absolution... your corpse will lie here beside mine FOREVER!",
        "Flags": "Standard",
        "Sound": "",
        "VolumeVariance": 0,
        "PitchVariance": 0,
        "Strref": 31514
      },
      "ResponsesIndexFirst": 7,
      "ResponsesCount": 1,
      "TriggerIndex": -1,
      "Index": 3
    },
    {
      "Text": {
        "Text": "AIEEE!  The light of your words - they burn my *soul!*  Damn your eyes, fiend - what has become of me?!",
        "Flags": "Standard",
        "Sound": "",
        "VolumeVariance": 0,
        "PitchVariance": 0,
        "Strref": 31516
      },
      "ResponsesIndexFirst": 8,
      "ResponsesCount": 3,
      "TriggerIndex": 1,
      "Index": 4
    },
    {
      "Text": {
        "Text": "How... how did this come to pass?",
        "Flags": "Standard",
        "Sound": "",
        "VolumeVariance": 0,
        "PitchVariance": 0,
        "Strref": 31520
      },
      "ResponsesIndexFirst": 11,
      "ResponsesCount": 3,
      "TriggerIndex": -1,
      "Index": 5
    },
    {
      "Text": {
        "Text": "Yes... *yes!*  It is my captors who should pay, not my companions of old.  The duergar will know my terrible vengeance, and then I shall finally know peace.  Farewell...",
        "Flags": "Standard",
        "Sound": "",
        "VolumeVariance": 0,
        "PitchVariance": 0,
        "Strref": 31523
      },
      "ResponsesIndexFirst": 14,
      "ResponsesCount": 1,
      "TriggerIndex": -1,
      "Index": 6
    },
    {
      "Text": {
        "Text": "I don't belong here... my companions are gone, even my captors of old are no more.  I will go, now... farewell.",
        "Flags": "Standard",
        "Sound": "",
        "VolumeVariance": 0,
        "PitchVariance": 0,
        "Strref": 31525
      },
      "ResponsesIndexFirst": 15,
      "ResponsesCount": 1,
      "TriggerIndex": -1,
      "Index": 7
    },
    {
      "Text": {
        "Text": "Farewell.",
        "Flags": "Standard",
        "Sound": "",
        "VolumeVariance": 0,
        "PitchVariance": 0,
        "Strref": 31526
      },
      "ResponsesIndexFirst": 16,
      "ResponsesCount": 1,
      "TriggerIndex": 0,
      "Index": 8
    }
  ],
  "Responses": [
    {
      "Text": {
        "Text": "What are you talking about?",
        "Flags": "Standard",
        "Sound": "",
        "VolumeVariance": 0,
        "PitchVariance": 0,
        "Strref": 8496
      },
      "JournalIndex": 0,
      "TriggerIndex": -1,
      "ActionIndex": -1,
      "NextScriptDialog": "51SPE",
      "NextPhraseIndex": 2,
      "Index": 0,
      "Flags": "HasText"
    },
    {
      "Text": {
        "Text": "You've mistaken me for another, spirit.  Farewell.",
        "Flags": "Standard",
        "Sound": "",
        "VolumeVariance": 0,
        "PitchVariance": 0,
        "Strref": 8497
      },
      "JournalIndex": 0,
      "TriggerIndex": -1,
